parameters: \nw[\N[21]]Oh, oh... Looks like you're having fun, huh?

\nw[Fross]Yes, it's very enjoyable. I haven't had the chance
to put Amor-sama's teachings into practice for a
long time.

\nw[\N[21]](Come to think of it, they say your personality
changes when you're in heat...)

\nw[\N[21]](I've heard stories about going into heat and
losing control, so maybe it'll be fine if I just
leave her alone.)
\nw[Fross]*slurp* *slurp*... It tastes like a man ♥ Mmm ♥
\nw[Man]Haa, haa, Amor religion is the best!

\nw[Male]What an outrageous girl... Even though I have a
wife, she's tempting me.

\nw[Man]Fine, I have no choice! I have no choice but to
entertain you.

\nw[Male]The Amor religion is the best. It's amazing to
think that there are such beautiful followers.
